I'm sorry, I don't have any in white.

147
00:15:22,212 --> 00:15:24,464
I know you have a job to do,
but please tell Patti

148
00:15:24,632 --> 00:15:27,050
she's wasting your time
sending you here.

149
00:15:27,217 --> 00:15:29,135
I've made it this far.

150
00:15:30,763 --> 00:15:32,263
I'm not gonna turn around now.

151
00:15:43,859 --> 00:15:45,568
What the hell?

152
00:15:50,157 --> 00:15:52,283
- What?
- Hello, Matt?

153
00:15:54,161 --> 00:15:56,162
Hey, Jim, is that you?

154
00:15:57,164 --> 00:15:59,666
I'm sorry.
My phone's been acting up.

155
00:16:01,710 --> 00:16:04,128
- How are you?
- Good. I'm good.

156
00:16:05,172 --> 00:16:08,675
Matt, I'm sure you're busy,
but can you come by the bank?

157
00:16:08,842 --> 00:16:10,635
- Sure.
- It's important.

158
00:16:10,761 --> 00:16:15,556
