for at least two weeks now.

164
00:16:41,333 --> 00:16:44,335
And you always knew
this could happen

165
00:16:44,503 --> 00:16:49,132
once you stopped making payments
and we had to foreclose.

166
00:16:50,884 --> 00:16:52,218
