Come on in.

191
00:19:23,036 --> 00:19:25,079
Doug won't mind. I promise.

192
00:19:34,756 --> 00:19:36,007
Is Mary okay?

193
00:19:37,217 --> 00:19:39,093
She's great.

194
00:19:42,055 --> 00:19:43,639
And what?

195
00:19:46,768 --> 00:19:49,770
I need to borrow $135,000.

196
00:19:51,899 --> 00:19:54,400
- What?
- They're gonna sell the church.

197
00:20:03,577 --> 00:20:04,911
I'm sorry.

198
00:20:09,875 --> 00:20:13,169
I know it's a lot of money,
but it'd just be a loan.

199
00:20:13,337 --> 00:20:15,588
Things are changing.
People are ready to come back.

200
00:20:15,714 --> 00:20:18,424
I just performed a baptism
this morning.

201
00:20:21,011 --> 00:20:24,722
I hate coming to you,
but this is our family church.

202
00:20:26,183 --> 00:20:28,684
- Mom and Dad's.
- No, Matt, it's your church.

203
00:20:28,852 --> 00:20:29,894
They left it to both of us.

204
00:20:30,062 --> 00:20:31,938
They didn't leave it to anyone.

205
00:20:32,105 --> 00:20:34,607
They died in a fire when I was seven
and then it was given--

206
00:20:34,733 --> 00:20:36,692
Please, don't get upset.

207
00:20:36,860 --> 00:20:39,278
- Why do you always have to do that?
- What?

208
00:20:39,446 --> 00:20:42,240
Make me upset
and then tell me not to get upset.

209
00:20:42,407 --> 00:20:44,617
You can't just knock on my door
and asked for $135,000--

210
00:20:44,743 --> 00:20:45,910
