and my children.

213
00:21:01,176 --> 00:21:02,301
I'm sorry.

214
00:21:04,471 --> 00:21:07,306
You're right.
I shouldn't have asked.

215
00:21:07,849 --> 00:21:11,310
I just didn't know where to go.

216
00:21:21,405 --> 00:21:26,117
- Will you stop making your paper?
- What?

217
00:21:26,285 --> 00:21:29,870
You're asking me for something,
I'm asking you for something.

218
00:21:30,914 --> 00:21:32,999
Stop making your paper
and I'll give you the money.

219
00:21:33,166 --> 00:21:34,333
- I can't do that.
- Why not?

220
00:21:34,501 --> 00:21:35,835
People need to hear the truth.

221
00:21:35,961 --> 00:21:37,378
People need to punch you in the face.

222
00:21:37,546 --> 00:21:39,797
